column3: Can someone with a mac test this?\n
Did any Mac user test this?\n
Is that even possible as long as we don't have Qt5 support?\n
@Diapolo Somewhat. The missing menu title is now set correctly. I'll see if I can get some screens of the before/after for the retina changes\n

Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/e37f82b8aa1d0f149855a35e2cd3d98fd6181586 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu

Shouldn't we also be adding
